name: The roar of the sea
description: I want the sea It seems to be somewhere between the water A land a few meters between the sea Preferably in the fall and the full moon, I sleep alone on a wet swim and close my eyes and drown in the sound of the sea so that I can not hear any sound, whether from my heart or from my mind. I am so overwhelmed that I forget everything, whether it is the regrets of yesterday or the worries of tomorrow. Take it easy
